  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/c15bbbb971240cf328aba572178f091684585468" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.338ex; width:1.232ex; height:1.676ex;" alt="\nu "/></span><span about="#mwt648">
</span> and transition from a lower energy <span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt661" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"E_{j}"}}' id="mwAfw"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle E_{j}}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">
        <msub>
          <mi>E</mi>
