  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/a01babf2293d37d9ff73b61202cfc3a3933eaf19" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -1.005ex; width:2.625ex; height:2.843ex;" alt="E_{j}"/></span><span about="#mwt661">
</span> to a higher energy <span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt667" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"E_{i}"}}' id="mwAf0"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle E_{i}}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">
        <msub>
          <mi>E</mi>
          <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mi>i</mi>
          </mrow>
