        <mo>,</mo>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\displaystyle g_{i}/g_{j}\exp {(E_{j}-E_{i})/(kT)},}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/dffee654ba7c336692545142574aa3990632752b" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -1.005ex; width:25.672ex; height:3.009ex;" alt="{\displaystyle g_{i}/g_{j}\exp {(E_{j}-E_{i})/(kT)},}"/></span><span about="#mwt703">
</span> where <span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt705" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"g_{i,j}"}}' id="mwAhk"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle g_{i,j}}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">
        <msub>
          <mi>g</mi>
          <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mi>i</mi>
            <mo>,</mo>
            <mi>j</mi>
          </mrow>
        </msub>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\displaystyle g_{i,j}}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/cb2fe270b32fba161f2f6faf9e14938ece246ce7" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -1.005ex; width:3.044ex; height:2.343ex;" alt="g_{i,j}"/></span><span about="#mwt705">
</span> are the <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Degenerate_energy_level" title="Degenerate energy level" id="mwAho" class="mw-redirect">degeneracy</a> of the state i and that of j, respectively, <span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt707" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"E_{i,j}"}}' id="mwAhs"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle E_{i,j}}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">
        <msub>
          <mi>E</mi>
          <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mi>i</mi>
            <mo>,</mo>
            <mi>j</mi>
          </mrow>
        </msub>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\displaystyle E_{i,j}}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/e7814421833a1b6fae2769bb795158a0c02ecda0" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -1.005ex; width:3.65ex; height:2.843ex;" alt="E_{i,j}"/></span><span about="#mwt707">
</span> their energies, k the <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Boltzmann_constant" title="Boltzmann constant" id="mwAhw">Boltzmann constant</a> and T the system's <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Temperature" title="Temperature" id="mwAh0">temperature</a>. From this, it is readily derived that
<span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt709" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"g_iB_{ij}=g_jB_{ji}"}}' id="mwAh4"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle g_{i}B_{ij}=g_{j}B_{ji}}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">
        <msub>
          <mi>g</mi>
          <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mi>i</mi>
          </mrow>
        </msub>
        <msub>
          <mi>B</mi>
          <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mi>i</mi>
            <mi>j</mi>
          </mrow>
        </msub>
        <mo>=</mo>
        <msub>
          <mi>g</mi>
          <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mi>j</mi>
          </mrow>
        </msub>
        <msub>
          <mi>B</mi>
          <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mi>j</mi>
            <mi>i</mi>
          </mrow>
        </msub>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\displaystyle g_{i}B_{ij}=g_{j}B_{ji}}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/b05f1a0bd93673e8867ac6c3728a2fd60108f6bc" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -1.005ex; width:13.508ex; height:2.843ex;" alt="g_iB_{ij}=g_jB_{ji}"/></span><span about="#mwt709">
</span> and</p>
<dl id="mwAh8"><dd id="mwAiA"><span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt711" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"\nA_{ij}=\\frac{8 \\pi h \\nu^{3}}{c^{3}} B_{ij}.\n"}}' id="mwAiE"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle A_{ij}={\frac {8\pi h\nu ^{3}}{c^{3}}}B_{ij}.}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">
        <msub>
          <mi>A</mi>
          <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mi>i</mi>
            <mi>j</mi>
          </mrow>
        </msub>
        <mo>=</mo>
        <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
          <mfrac>
            <mrow>
              <mn>8</mn>
              <mi>π<!-- π --></mi>
              <mi>h</mi>
              <msup>
                <mi>ν<!-- ν --></mi>
                <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
                  <mn>3</mn>
                </mrow>
              </msup>
            </mrow>
            <msup>
              <mi>c</mi>
              <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
                <mn>3</mn>
              </mrow>
            </msup>
          </mfrac>
        </mrow>
        <msub>
          <mi>B</mi>
