</span> photons are in the mode <span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt1005" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"k_i"}}' id="mwAns"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle k_{i}}">
