</span>. In this notation, the creation of a new photon in mode <span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt1007" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"k_i"}}' id="mwAnw"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle k_{i}}">
