</span> (e.g., emitted from an atomic transition) is written as <span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt1009" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"|n_{k_i}\\rangle \\rightarrow|n_{k_i}+1\\rangle"}}' id="mwAn0"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle |n_{k_{i}}\rangle \rightarrow |n_{k_{i}}+1\rangle }">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
