t43" id="mwA8M"/><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt43" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}' id="mwA8Q"/></span></li><li about="#cite_note-15" id="cite_note-15"><a href="./Photon#cite_ref-15" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-15" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation journal" about="#mwt44" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite journal ","href":"./Template:Cite_journal"},"params":{"last":{"wt":"Villard"},"first":{"wt":"P."},"authorlink":{"wt":"Paul Ulrich Villard"},"year":{"wt":"1900"},"title":{"wt":"Sur le rayonnement du radium"},"journal":{"wt":"[[Comptes Rendus des Séances de l&apos;Académie des Sciences]]"},"volume":{"wt":"130"},"pages":{"wt":"1178–1179"},"language":{"wt":"fr"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwA8U"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Paul_Ulrich_Villard" title="Paul Ulrich Villard" id="mwA8Y">Villard, P.</a> (1900). "Sur le rayonnement du radium". <i id="mwA8c"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Comptes_Rendus_des_Séances_de_l'Académie_des_Sciences" title="Comptes Rendus des Séances de l'Académie des Sciences" id="mwA8g" class="mw-redirect">Comptes Rendus des Séances de l'Académie des Sciences</a></i> (in French). <b id="mwA8k">130</b>: 1178–1179.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Comptes+Rendus+des+S%C3%A9ances+de+l%27Acad%C3%A9mie+des+Sciences&amp;rft.atitle=Sur+le+rayonnement+du+radium&amp;rft.volume=130&amp;rft.pages=1178-1179&amp;rft.date=1900&amp;rft.aulast=Villard&amp;rft.aufirst=P.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APhoton" class="Z3988" about="#mwt44" id="mwA8o"></span><link rel="mw:PageProp/Category" href="./Category:CS1_French-language_sources_(fr)" about="#mwt44" id="mwA8s"/><li