XA">ISBN</a><span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwBXE"> </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Special:BookSources/978-0-07-055287-6" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-07-055287-6" id="mwBXI">978-0-07-055287-6</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Quantum+Mechanics&amp;rft.edition=3rd&amp;rft.pub=McGraw-Hill&amp;rft.date=1968&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-07-055287-6&amp;rft.aulast=Schiff&amp;rft.aufirst=L.I.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APhoton" class="Z3988" about="#mwt253" id="mwBXM"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt253" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}' id="mwBXQ"/></span></li><li about="#cite_note-68" id="cite_note-68"><a href="./Photon#cite_ref-68" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-68" class="mw-reference-text">
